<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<title>K Crochets</title>

<style>
body {
  background: linear-gradient(#ffe4ec, #fff);
  font-family: Arial;
  text-align: center;
  margin: 0;
}

header {
  background: #ffb6c1;
  padding: 30px;
  border-bottom: 5px dotted white;
}

h1 {
  margin: 0;
  color: white;
  font-size: 40px;
}

h2 {
  color: #ff69b4;
}

.section {
  padding: 25px;
}

img {
  width: 180px;
  border-radius: 25px;
  margin: 10px;
  box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
  transition: transform 0.2s;
}

img:hover {
  transform: scale(1.08);
}

.card {
  background: white;
  margin: 20px auto;
  padding: 20px;
  border-radius: 25px;
  width: 85%;
  max-width: 500px;
  box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
}

footer {
  margin-top: 20px;
  padding: 15px;
  background: #ffb6c1;
  color: white;
}
</style>

</head>

<body>

<header>
  <h1>🧶 K Crochets</h1>
  <p><b>Plushies for Everyone 💕</b></p>
</header>

<div class="card">
  <h2>🌊 Ocean Buddies</h2>
  <img src="IMG2355.jpeg">
</div>. 
